OL,3,CAmbulance chief warns people to 'drink
OL,4,Cresponsibly' as sweltering heat
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FA chief at the country's largest
OL,8,Fambulance service has warned people to
OL,9,Fdrink responsibly and avoid exercising
OL,10,Foutside amid a punishing heatwave
OL,11,Fwhich has seen record-breaking
OL,12,Ftemperatures for June.
OL,14,FThe country sweltered in exceptionally
OL,15,Fhot and humid weather for a second
OL,16,Fconsecutive day on Thursday, with rare
OL,17,Fred weather warnings continuing into
OL,18,FFriday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
