FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782436704
OL,3,CAmbulance chief warns people to 'drink
OL,4,Cresponsibly' as sweltering heat
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FThe Met Office said temperatures had
OL,8,Freached 36.7C in Merryfield, Somerset,
OL,9,Fon Thursday afternoon, provisionally
OL,10,Fmaking it the UK's hottest June day on
OL,11,Frecord.
OL,13,FSchools and nurseries have been forced
OL,14,Fto closed and a hosepipe ban has been
OL,15,Fbrought in for Kent amid surging
OL,16,Fdemand.
OL,18,FTransport services have been disrupted
OL,19,Fand one rail operator has urged people
OL,20,Fnot to travel for beach trips because
OL,21,Fof the extreme heat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
