OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782436704
OL,3,CAmbulance chief warns people to 'drink
OL,4,Cresponsibly' as sweltering heat
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FA 50-year-old man from from Cilfrew,
OL,8,FNeath Port Talbot, Wales, died after
OL,9,Fentering the water at Aberavon beach
OL,10,Fon Wednesday, police said.
OL,12,FOn Thursday evening, firefighters in
OL,13,FDerbyshire continued battling a 500
OL,14,Fsquare metre wildfire on Tintwistle
OL,15,FMoor, with video showing billowing
OL,16,Fsmoke and flames consuming trees.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
