OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782436704
OL,3,CAmbulance chief warns people to 'drink
OL,4,Cresponsibly' as sweltering heat
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FSeveral hospitals have declared
OL,8,Fcritical incidents amid the heatwave,
OL,9,Fwith University Hospital Southampton
OL,10,Fbeing forced to cancel a number of
OL,11,Fplanned operations and some outpatient
OL,12,Fappointments.
OL,14,FQueen Alexandra Hospital in Portsmouth
OL,15,Fand Norfolk and Norwich University
OL,16,FHospitals NHS Foundation Trust both
OL,17,Fdeclared critical incidents on
OL,18,FWednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
