CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782436704
OL,3,CAmbulance chief warns people to 'drink
OL,4,Cresponsibly' as sweltering heat
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FThe London Ambulance Service (LAS)
OL,8,Fresponded to its highest number of
OL,9,Flife-threatening emergencies ever on
OL,10,FWednesday, and its chief operating
OL,11,Fofficer Craig Harman said they expect
OL,12,F"demand to grow day on day over the
OL,13,Fnext couple of days".
OL,15,FAs football fans prepare to cheer for
OL,16,FEngland during Saturday's Fifa World
OL,17,FCup game, Mr Harman has told people to
OL,18,Fdrink responsibly. He advised people
OL,19,Fto drink "plenty of water" in between
OL,20,Falcoholic beverages.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@TO]{D@JOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782436704
OL,3,CAmbulance chief warns people to 'drink
OL,4,Cresponsibly' as sweltering heat
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FThe chief told the Press Association
OL,8,Fthat it is not just the elderly and
OL,9,Fpeople with underlying health
OL,10,Fconditions affected by the heat,
OL,11,Fadding: "I'm saying to people I need
OL,12,Fyou to drink water even when you're
OL,13,Fnot thirsty, staying out of the sun
OL,14,Fduring the hottest parts of the day,
OL,15,Fand particularly not exercising
OL,16,Foutside and putting your body under
OL,17,Fadditional heat and strain."
OL,26,@sD@IOUyD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
