OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782436704
OL,3,CAmbulance chief warns people to 'drink
OL,4,Cresponsibly' as sweltering heat
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FLAS saw a 50% increase in life-
OL,8,Fthreatening emergency calls compared
OL,9,Fwith a typical Wednesday in June, with
OL,10,Fthe number of cardiac arrests up 30%.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, London Mayor Sir Sadiq Khan
OL,13,Fhas said air conditioning should be
OL,14,Frolled out to schools, offices and
OL,15,Fhospitals in the capital as it adapts
OL,16,Fto more intense and frequent
OL,17,Fheatwaves, as he launched the city's
OL,18,Ffirst heat plan to keep Londoners safe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
