OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782436704
OL,3,CAmbulance chief warns people to 'drink
OL,4,Cresponsibly' as sweltering heat
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FThe current heatwave is driven by a
OL,8,F"heat-dome" ` an area of high pressure
OL,9,Fthat stalls over a region and traps
OL,10,Fheat ` settling over western Europe
OL,11,Fand bringing extreme conditions across
OL,12,Fthe continent.
OL,14,FHuman-driven climate change, mostly
OL,15,Fcaused by burning fossil fuels, is
OL,16,Fmaking such extreme heatwaves more
OL,17,Ffrequent and intense.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
