OL,3,CAmbulance chief warns people to 'drink
OL,4,Cresponsibly' as sweltering heat
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FEarlier, the Met Office extended its
OL,8,Fred warning until 9pm on Friday for
OL,9,FLondon and parts of east and South
OL,10,FEast England, stretching across
OL,11,FOxfordshire and Bedfordshire,
OL,12,FHampshire and Kent ` the first time it
OL,13,Fhas issued red heat warnings over
OL,14,Fthree consecutive days.
OL,16,FAmber heat warnings are in place for a
OL,17,Fwider area on Friday, and are running
OL,18,Finto Saturday for parts of east and
OL,19,Fsouth-east England.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
